HEADWORD: Burglarious
<hw>Bur*gla"ri*ous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to
burglary; constituting the crime of burglary.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To come down a chimney is held a <qex>burglarious</qex> entry.</q>
